reviewText: this episode is really good and shows how teamwork can accomplish anything.  Team Cherokee is a racing team that is sabotaged several times to keep them from racing but they keep coming back ready to race.  After the driver is hurt Walker takes over as the driver and there is two great races one at the beginning and one at the end.  Also in this episode a little girl is kidnapped but when she is found a startling discovery is made.
jimmy wleck really outdid himself in this movie.  A great show!

I had the pleasure to watch this episode while it was on tv, and although I have to admit one of the major reasons I watched it was because of Jimmy Wlcek, I have to admit this episode ROCKS!  I highly recommend it to any  and all Walker fans.
